\begin_inset Formula $\vec{u}$
\end_inset

-column degrees bounded by 
\begin_inset Formula $\vec{v}$
\end_inset

 if and only if its 
\begin_inset Formula $-\vec{v}$
\end_inset

-row degrees are bounded by 
\begin_inset Formula $-\vec{u}$
\end_inset

